column5: We are headed up to Minaki on Saturday morning and we are looking for any fishing reports that any body may have or any fishing info or a road report. Thanks for any information that anyone may have. Also are the Muskies doing any action. THANKS AGAIN!

If you go to muskiecentral there is a post about the fishing. I myself had a ok trip for the opener of muskies. The walleye fish I heard had slowed. lots of luck and please post how you do. for I am going back in august. thanks bill
Hey haven't heard from ya just how was the trip anyway?
